Class GlobeAnimateRotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mousebird.maply.GlobeAnimateRotation

  • public class GlobeAnimateRotation
extends java.lang.Object
    Implements a rotation with momentum on the globe.

    In general, the MaplyController creates these and you'd only be doing so yourself if you've subclassed it.
